00:32:57.434 --> 00:32:59.602
I'll prescribe danggui buxue decoction

00:32:59.603 --> 00:33:02.022
To enrich his blood and replenish his energy.

00:33:02.772 --> 00:33:06.526
Tomorrow, you can take the first ferry back to the mainland to get it treated.

00:33:08.653 --> 00:33:09.654
Okay.

